items.badge_name: Dubbel, Tripel and Quad Oh My! (Level 7)
items.badge_description: Dubbel, Tripel, or Quad, you can’t go wrong with these amazing feats of Belgian style brewing. Whether you’re looking for something light and golden or dark and boozy, one of these will do the trick! That's 35 different beers with the style of Dubbel, Tripel or Quad! Try 5 more for Level 8!

items.checkin_comment: Absolutely delicious. One of the best Belgian triples I've had. Sweet, thick & velvety.

user.bio: Seattle game producer, craft beer lover, and home brewer. Find me on Instagram under bourbon_and_brew.

items.checkin_comment: Tastes more like like a brown Which isn't bad but no tripel
